	<a class="aw-user-name hidden-xs" data-id="350" href="http://openskill.cn/people/chris" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://openskill.cn/uploads/avatar/000/00/03/50_avatar_max.jpg" alt="" /></a>	<div class="aw-question-content">
                 <h4>
                                                
                        
                                                <a href="http://openskill.cn/question/513">静态编译报错：/usr/bin/ld: cannot find -lc</a>
                                        </h4> 
				<div class="pull-right hidden-xs contribute">
			<span class="pull-right text-color-999">贡献</span>
		    		    <a class="aw-user-name" data-id="1" href="http://openskill.cn/people/WaterSpinach" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://openskill.cn/uploads/avatar/000/00/00/01_avatar_mid.jpg" alt="" /></a>
